These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, blueberry, garlic
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, scrabble, mah-jongg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, biathlon, handball, baseball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person playing chess##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the person playing canasta is between the person who's sport is handball and the person eating asparagus##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | blueberry | garlic  | asparagus | artichoke  |
| Game         | mah-jongg    | canasta  | chess       | scrabble     |
| Sport   | handball     | water-polo | baseball       | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
City: berlin, nizza, hamburg, venice
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, snake, fish
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the fish is between the person traveling to venice and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person traveling to venice is the owner of the pony##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| City   | venice  | berlin  | nizza   | hamburg    |
| Pet         | pony | fish | hedgehog | snake      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
House: futuristic, art-deco, townhouse, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
There 4 different types of food: pear, grapes, asparagus, corn
1. the person eating grapes is between the person eating corn and the art-deco house##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person eating pear##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the person eating pear is on the right of the futuristic house##1
7. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| House      | art-deco | gothic-revival         | futuristic   | townhouse    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| Food   | asparagus   | grapes        | corn      | pear   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, goldfish, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, skateboarding, tennis
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, photography, woodworking, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the owner of the mouse##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | mouse        | lizard   | guinea-pig | goldfish |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cricket | cycling    | tennis |
| Hobby     | woodworking       | video-games     | traveling       | photography    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade, tea
4 different games are played: whist, billiard, poker, chess
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, taxi, boat
1. the person driving the boat is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person driving the boat is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the taxi and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| Game      | whist   | billiard  | chess | poker     |
| Transport      | train     | boat | taxi        | skateboard |

