.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, designer, bartender, writer
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, british, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, swimming
1. the australian is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the teacher is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the teacher is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the designer##1
5. the brazilian is between the australian and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the designer is between the teacher and the bartender##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Job    | bartender | designer  | teacher | writer      |
| Nationality   | british  | australian  | brazilian | canadian |
| Sport   | swimming | ice-hockey | rowing | soccer     |

