.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, papaya, pepper, pomegranate
House: palace, victorian, farmhouse, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, juice, milk
1. the person drinking milk is the victorian house##1
2. the person drinking juice is the palace house##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
4. the art-deco house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating papaya is between the victorian house and the farmhouse house##2
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper  | papaya    | pomegranate | lettuce  |
| House   | farmhouse | art-deco       | victorian        | palace    |
| Beverage         | sprite | 7up | milk  | juice |

