.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, cooking, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, rowing, climbing, soccer
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, british, polish, indian
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the russian##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the indian and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the polish##1
4. the polish is on the right of the russian##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| Sport   | skiing  | soccer | rowing   | climbing         |
| Nationality           | russian | polish  | british   | indian      |

