.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, mango, pepper, tomato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, zombie, spy, romance
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, baccarat, siglo, swisher
1. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is the person eating eggplant##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person watching spy movies is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is between the siglo-smoker and the person watching musical movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | tomato  | eggplant    | pepper | mango       |
| Movie-Genre         | romance | zombie | musical  | spy |
| Cigar   | siglo   | swisher      | baccarat  | game     |

