1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the wooden house is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the wooden house is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
7. the modern house is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the futuristic house is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
