.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, colombian, indonesian, dutch
City: marseilles, edinburgh, hannover, london
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is the person eating garlic##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is between the colombian and the indonesian##2
4. the indonesian is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the indonesian is the person traveling to london##1
6. the polish is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
7. the dutch is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| Nationality   | polish | indonesian   | dutch  | colombian    |
| City     | edinburgh        | london       | marseilles      | hannover |

