.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, october, january
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
There 4 different types of food: peach, garlic, apricot, radish
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
6. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
7. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday   | january | october     | july | december       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Food        | radish  | garlic      | apricot        | peach      |

