.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, disco, ambient, r&b
House: modern, futuristic, townhouse, gothic-revival
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rabbit
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the fan of ambient and the modern house##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
4. the fan of trance is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the futuristic house##1
6. the fan of r&b is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance | r&b  | ambient       | disco   |
| House      | modern     | townhouse | futuristic | gothic-revival |
| Pet        | pony        | rabbit | ferret     | hamster |

