.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, entrepreneur, mechanic, scientist
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, reading, drawing, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, tennis, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the mechanic##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the mechanic##2
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | scientist | mechanic    | dancer   |
| Hobby   | drawing      | reading   | skydiving | card-games |
| Sport     | climbing     | golf       | tennis        | swimming    |

