The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour, rugby, sailing
1. the fan of d&b is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of trance is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's birthday is in july and the fan of trance##2
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | indie           | trance         | reggae      |
| Birthday     | july | december | october | june |
| Sport   | rugby     | parkour         | biathlon       | sailing        |

