.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bolivar, aristoff, game
There 4 different types of food: kale, plum, asparagus, artichoke
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, italian, mexican
1. the person eating kale is the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the indian##2
3. the aristoff-smoker is the person eating plum##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is between the person eating asparagus and the mexican##2
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
6. the german is between the italian and the person eating artichoke##2
7. the person eating kale is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar      | bolivar | aristoff | tiparillo   | game |
| Food   | kale  | plum    | asparagus   | artichoke     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | italian | german | indian   |

