.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, train, trike, airplane
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, kiwi, lime, orange
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, trance, d&b, soul
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is between the person driving the airplane and the fan of d&b##2
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of trance##1
4. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person driving the train##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person driving the trike is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Transport   | bus    | train | airplane           | trike |
| Food       | artichoke | lime    | kiwi          | orange   |
| Music-Genre      | d&b  | trance   | soul | indie  |

