.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, monopoly, backgammon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, romance, sports
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, amaryllis, rose, zinnia
1. the person watching romance movies is the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing chess is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person who growszinnia is between the person playing snooker and the person who growsmarigold##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Game      | monopoly | chess | snooker     | backgammon   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports        | romance  | epic  |
| Flower           | marigold      | zinnia         | amaryllis | rose |

