The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, snowboarding, surfing, weightlifting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, animation, action, documentary
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person watching action movies is the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person watching action movies##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person watching action movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Cigar         | old-henry        | fonseca  | swisher | bluemaster   |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | surfing    | snowboarding |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery        | action     | documentary       | animation      |

