.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, daffodil, rose, dahlia
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, cola, fanta
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, skateboard
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person who growsdahlia and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Flower        | dahlia | daffodil | marigold | rose |
| Beverage         | milk       | hot-chocolate     | cola   | fanta   |
| Transport   | helicopter | jet-ski | motorbike | skateboard |

 